### ==========================================
### 👤 PROFILE ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### Get Public Profile by ID
GET http://localhost:6868/api/profile/USER_ID_HERE

###

### Update My Profile (must be logged in)
PUT http://localhost:6868/api/profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Karthik",
    "lastName": "Engili",
    "bio": "Full-stack developer passionate about building real-world applications.",
    "skills": "React, Node.js, MongoDB, Express, TailwindCSS"
}

###

### Upload Avatar (must be logged in)
### Note: Use form-data in Postman/Thunder Client for file upload
PUT http://localhost:6868/api/profile/avatar
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="avatar"; filename="avatar.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test-avatar.png
--boundary--

###
